%h1
	Please sign in to continue

%p
	Note that login through the webportal makes use of Yggdrasil authentication via mojang. Using this may leave you signed out of other related services.
%p
	Additional Note: Mojang's servers are severely rate limited. If you can't sign in now, try again in a few minutes.

.center
	= form_tag(session_path, method: :post) do |f|
		= hidden_field_tag :from, params[:from]
		%table
			%tr
				%td
					= label_tag :username
					= text_field_tag :username
			%tr
				%td
					= label_tag :password
					= password_field_tag :password
			%tr
				%td(colspan="2")= submit_tag("Login")
